# =============================================================================
# .repomixignore — Repomix-only exclusions (Matryca Plumber)
# =============================================================================
# Complements repomix.config.json `include` allowlist, .gitignore, and Repomix
# default patterns. Goal: pack only source + tests + operator docs needed to
# understand and evaluate the codebase.
# Docs: https://repomix.com/guide/configuration
#
# Include allowlist (repomix.config.json) targets graph-derived core modules:
# Graph, Agent, Daemon, Cli, Semantic, Tana, Frontend, Tests (+ openspec docs).
# =============================================================================

# --- Repomix output (avoid recursive packs) ---
repomix-output.*
.repomix-cache/

# --- Secrets & local operator config ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
matryca-wiki.yml

# --- Runtime / daemon state (not source) ---
